Package com.qualcomm.hardware.bosch

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BNO055IMU
    BNO055IMU interface abstracts the functionality of the Bosch/Sensortec BNO055 Intelligent 9-axis absolute orientation sensor.
    BNO055IMU.AccelerationIntegrator
    BNO055IMU.AccelerationIntegrator encapsulates an algorithm for integrating acceleration information over time to produce velocity and position.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BNO055IMU.CalibrationData
    See Section 3.6.4 of the BNO055 Specification.
    BNO055IMU.CalibrationStatus  
    BNO055IMU.Parameters
    Instances of Parameters contain data indicating how a BNO055 absolute orientation sensor is to be initialized.
    BNO055IMUImpl
    BNO055IMUImpl provides support for communicating with a BNO055 inertial motion unit.
    BNO055IMUImpl.VectorData  
    JustLoggingAccelerationIntegrator
    JustLoggingAccelerationIntegrator is an integrator that doesn't actually integrate accelerations, but merely reports them in the logcat log.
    NaiveAccelerationIntegrator
    NaiveAccelerationIntegrator provides a very naive implementation of an acceleration integration algorithm.
